  "texts": [
    "The SST-2 dataset encompasses thoroughly annotated sentiment parse tree corpora.",
    "Extracted from movie reviews and parsed using the Stanford parser, the annotations are conducted at the sentence level by three annotators.",
    "The reviews are categorized into positive and negative sentiments.",
    "The dataset is included in GLUE as an evaluation benchmark for English NLU tasks.",
    "• AFQMC (Xu et al, 2020b)."
  ],
